    "player_approval": "Highly disapprove"
}

{
    "player_reason": "You agreed to help Minthara raid the Emerald Grove—betraying the tiefling refugees and druids, children among them—for the Absolute’s favor. That’s cruelty and treachery the Blade of Frontiers cannot abide.",
