{
    "player_reason": "You showed courage by challenging Gortash’s sham coronation and calling out the Absolute’s plot. I can’t approve of labeling my father a willing conspirator—if he’s involved, he’s under their control and needs saving—but your stand against Gortash is righteous.",
    "player_approval": "Approve"
